  "message": "chore(beads): consolidate issue tracker and clean up migration artifacts\n\nDeduplicate 146 duplicate entries in issues.jsonl, normalize issue IDs\nto dot-separated hierarchical format (e.g., coding_agent_session_search-1mfw3.1),\nand absorb bd-* prefixed issues from base_snapshot.jsonl into the canonical\nfile. Compact 81 old closed issues (streaming indexing, preview server,\ndeployment, integration tests) to reduce file size.\n\nRemove stale migration artifacts that are no longer needed:\n- base_snapshot.jsonl: migration source data now absorbed into issues.jsonl\n- issues.jsonl.backup: stale backup superseded by current state\n- issues.jsonl.pre_analytics_20260206T0656Z: pre-analytics migration snapshot\n- issues.jsonl.pre_id_migration_20260127T021505Z: pre-ID-migration snapshot\n- sync_base.jsonl: sync baseline data absorbed into canonical file\n\nAll deleted files are preserved in git history if needed for reference.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
